Science ka break-up ho chuka hai, aur dimaag buffer mode pe hai! Are you ready for this rollercoaster of nonsense? Buckle up and watch NOW! 

Meet Vaid Natwar Lal – the ultimate expert in jadibooti ka gyaan, whose solutions are weirder than the problems themselves! From bizarre home remedies to wisdom that defies all logic, this vaid ji will leave you questioning reality… and laughing till your stomach hurts
